Usage: add_interposer_route_block [-help] -cell <string> -inst <string>
                                  -location {x y}
                                  -orient {R0 R90 R180 R270 MX MY MX90 MY90}

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>     # specifies the master cell name that need to be repeated
                   # (string, required)
-inst <string>     # specifies the clone block name (string, required)
-location {x y}    # specifies the clone block's origin location
                   # (point, required)
-orient {R0 R90 R180 R270 MX MY MX90 MY90}
                   # specifies the orientation of the clone block compared with
                   # the master (enum, required)